                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17690906-8-victim114 t17690906-8-viclabel42"></join>. The prisoner came to my house on the 12th of July, about six in the evening, to enquire for a companion of his, that worked at my house, and we all went to drink together. By the prisoner's conversation I found he was going upon a furloe to see his friends. He is a <rs id="t17690906-8-deflabel43" type="occupation">fife</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17690906-8-defend111 t17690906-8-deflabel43"></join>. When we were at the <placeName id="t17690906-8-crimeloc44">Bell in Pye-street, Westminster</placeName>
